<body class="bodyStyle">
  <div style="padding-left:15px">
  <br/>
   <img width="580" src="data:image/png;base64,$coverLetterHeader" />
  </div>
  <div class="wtrMark">

    <div class="wtrMarkCnt">
      <div>
        <div style="padding-bottom: 1px;">
          <div style="padding-left:20px">
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <span style="font-weight: bold;">$timeNow</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <span style="font-weight: bold;">To</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <span>$sponsorName</span>
            <br/>
            <span>$parishName</span>
            <br/>
            <span>$parishCity</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <span style="font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;">Greetings from the Sinai Mar Thoma Center, New York</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
              #if( $totalCount == 1 )
		          #set($c_word1 = 'child')
		          #set($c_word2 = 'the')
		          #set($c_word3= 'A')
		      #else
			    #set($c_word1 = 'children')
			    #set($c_word2 = 'these')
			    #set($c_word3= 'Few')
			#end
            <span>We would like to express our gratitude to you for being a part of the Light to Life Mission and 
            sponsoring $totalCount $c_word1. Your support has enabled $c_word2 $c_word1 to attend church-based development 
            programs that is altering the quality of their lives while building up the children&#39;s self-esteemand enabling 
            them to hope for a brighter future.</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <br/>

            <span>Although we would love for every child to complete our program, regrettably, some children(s) leave the
             program early due to their altered circumstances. $c_word3 $c_word1 under your sponsorship had to leave the program and 
             we have provided an alternate $c_word1 in place of that child. The information of the new child has been included 
             with this letter.</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <br/>

            <span>If you have any questions or need any clarification, kindly contact the office of the Mar Thoma 
            Mission Board by email: marthomamissionboard@gmail.com or  phone +1(516)377-3311.</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <br/>

            <span>May God bless you and your family.</span>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <br/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
